N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 102.3 - Responsibility for examinations

State Regulations

Building principals are responsible for administering
department examinations and maintaining the integrity of examination content
and programs, in accordance with directions and procedures established by the
commissioner. Notes
